Y '''Lea Salonga-Chien''' (mibait '''Maria Lea Carmen Imutan Salonga''' inyang [[Pebreru 22]], [[1971]] king [[Angeles Lakanbalen]] king [[Pampanga]]) metung yang [[Tony Awards|Tony Award]]-menyambut a [[Filipino people|Filipinu]] [[manganta]] at [[actor|artista]] nung nu bantug ya keng kayang pamilarawan kang Kim king [[musical]] ''[[Miss Saigon]]''.  King parang ning [[musical theater]], ala nang aliwang [[Filipinu]ng menikua keng kayang pangabantug panginternational kalupa nang Salonga. Iya ing mumunang diling menikuang dakal a internationa a galal para keng metung mung linage o pamanarti. 

Iya ing mumunang [[Asian]] a lageng [[Eponine]] king musical a ''[[Les Misérables (musical)|Les Misérables]]'' king [[Broadway]], at maka tutuk yang maging tala bilang Fantine manibat [[Marsu 6]], [[2007]]. Inyang [[Pebreru 11]], [[2007]], lalage ya king [[Philippine International Convention Center]] kambe da ring [[Philippine Philharmonic Orchestra]]. 

Y Lea kapilan pamu pepalual ne ing kayang mumunang studio album kaibat ning 7 banua a inaus dang "Inspired".  Ing magdalang masolusolu ya mu rin ing pigawa a Beverly Craven's "Promise Me".

==Bie Kayanakan==
Y Lea Salonga mibait ya kang Feliciano Genuino Salonga at Ligaya Alcantara Imutan. Migdatun ya anam a banua inyang kayanakan na king [[Angeles Lakanbalen]], [[Pampanga]], bayu ya linipat [[Menila]].

Y Salonga meging yang maluid a anak a tala king [[Filipinas]]. Inyang pitu yang banua migprofessional debut lalage king musical ''[[The King and I]]'' neng [[Repertory Philippines]]. Iya ing menimunung tala king ''[[Annie]]'' at mikyabe ya karing aliwang productions, kalupa ning: ''[[Cat On A Hot Tin Roof]]'', ''[[Fiddler on the Roof]]'', ''[[The Rose Tattoo]]'', ''[[The Sound Of Music]]'', ''[[The Goodbye Girl]]'', ''[[Paper Moon (film)|Paper Moon]]'' at ''[[The Fantasticks]]''.


Megumpisa yang anak a tala, a iya ing meging talatanggap keng sarili nang television show, ''Love, Lea,'' at iya ing memuklat para kang [[Stevie Wonder]] inyang concert na inyang 1998 king [[Menila]]. Menikua yang atlung galal a  ''Aliw Awards'' para ''Best Child Performer'' manibat 1981 anggang 1983. Inyang 1983, inyang sophomore album, "Lea" linual ya. Meging tala ya naman king lage nang variety show nang [[German Moreno]] a miki pamansag a ''[[That's Entertainment]]''.  Ing anak a LeaT linage ya naman kayabe ne y [[Herbert Bautista]] dakal a makapamilyang Filipino films inyang katataulian ning 1980s kalupa ning ''Ninja Kids'', ''Captain Barbell'' at ''Pik Pak Boom''.

